# Public publishing boundary.
#
# This repository should only expose the public article surface:
# - README.md
# - articles/**
# - images/**
#
# Everything else in the production workspace remains local/private.

*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!index.md
!robots.txt
!sitemap.xml
!_config.yml
!_layouts/
!_layouts/**
!llms.txt
!articles/
!articles/**
!images/
!images/**
